 can be sustained at the volumes required for the EDM\nexperiment, about 60% of the design goal. These results are likely limited by\nthe low pressure that must be maintained above the superfluid bath.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Mar 2006 23:05:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
